<bibRefCitation author="Perez-Farrera, M. A. &amp; Vovides, A. P. &amp; Martinez-Camilo, R. &amp; Martinez-Melendez, N. &amp; Iglesias, C." box="[1061,1346,907,933]" pageId="11" pageNumber="439" pagination="433 - 443" refId="ref10238" refString="Perez-Farrera, M. A., Vovides, A. P., Martinez-Camilo, R., Martinez-Melendez, N. &amp; Iglesias, C. (2009) A reassessment of the Ceratozamia miqueliana species complex (Zamiaceae) of southeastern Mexico, with comments on species relationships. Systematics and Biodiversity, 7, 433 - 443. https: // doi. org / 10.1017 / S 1477200009990211" type="journal article" year="2009">
